uation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>path</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">d</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>M30,30 L30,90 M60,30 L60,90 M90,30 L90,90<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n          <span class=\"token attr-name\">stroke</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>white<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p><strong>实时样例</strong></p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-linecap/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>stroke-linecap</code> 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#shape\" title=\"en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#Shape\">图形元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element#TextContent\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用背景","id":"使用背景"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性 参照主页","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stroke-linecap","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stroke-linecap","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"stroke-linecap","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"stroke-linecap","locale":"ru","native":"Р